                  <div>
                   <div class="yTFeqb wp-ms oJxARb nBWfrd i8qq8b" data-hveid="CFoQAA">
                    <div class="WFxqwc OTFaAf">
                     <div class="xGj8Mb">
                      <div class="wDYxhc" data-hveid="CFAQAA" data-md="50" data-ved="2ahUKEwiF7_GbwruFAxX8i68BHWE0DTsQkCl6BAhQEAA" style="clear:none">
                       <div class="PZPZlf hb8SAc" data-attrid="description" data-hveid="CFAQAQ" data-ved="2ahUKEwiF7_GbwruFAxX8i68BHWE0DTsQziAoAHoECFAQAQ">
                        <div jsaction="SKAaMe:c0XUbe;rcuQ6b:npT2md" jscontroller="GCSbhd">
                         <div class="kno-rdesc" jsaction="seM7Qe:c0XUbe;Iigoee:c0XUbe;rcuQ6b:npT2md" jscontroller="GCSbhd">
                          <h3 class="bNg8Rb OhScic zsYMMe BBwThe" style="clip:rect(1px,1px,1px,1px);height:1px;overflow:hidden;position:absolute;white-space:nowrap;width:1px;z-index:-1000;-webkit-user-select:none">
                           설명
                          </h3>
                          <span>
                           <span>
                            탕수육은 돼지고기에 녹말튀김옷을 입혀서 튀긴 것에 달고 새콤한 탕수 소스를 곁들여 먹는 한국식 중국요리다. 탕수 소스는 설탕, 식초, 야채, 녹말물 등을 기본으로 하여 끓여서 만든다.
                           </span>
                          </span>
                          <span>
                           <span>
                           </span>
                           <a class="ruhjFe NJLBac fl" data-ved="2ahUKEwiF7_GbwruFAxX8i68BHWE0DTsQmhN6BAhQEAI" href="https://ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/%ED%83%95%EC%88%98%EC%9C%A1" ping="/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;opi=89978449&amp;url=https://ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/%25ED%2583%2595%25EC%2588%2598%25EC%259C%25A1&amp;ved=2ahUKEwiF7_GbwruFAxX8i68BHWE0DTsQmhN6BAhQEAI">
                            <span>
                             위키백과
                            </span>
                           </a>
                          </span>
                         </div>
                        </div>
                       </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="wDYxhc" data-attrid="hw:/collection/dishes:origin" data-hveid="CFEQAA" data-md="1001" data-ved="2ahUKEwiF7_GbwruFAxX8i68BHWE0DTsQkCl6BAhREAA" style="clear:none">
                       <div class="Z1hOCe">
                        <div class="zloOqf PZPZlf" data-ved="2ahUKEwiF7_GbwruFAxX8i68BHWE0DTsQyxMoAHoECFEQAQ">
                         <div class="rVusze">
                          <span class="w8qArf">
                           <a class="fl" data-ved="2ahUKEwiF7_GbwruFAxX8i68BHWE0DTsQ6BMoAHoECFEQAg" href="/search?sca_esv=221f3c1ac0fa11b3&amp;sca_upv=1&amp;q=%ED%83%95%EC%88%98%EC%9C%A1+%EC%9B%90%EC%82%B0%EC%A7%80&amp;stick=H4sIAAAAAAAAAAFFALr_CA4SDS9nLzExYmM1d2RkN20qHGh3Oi9jb2xsZWN0aW9uL2Rpc2hlczpvcmlnaW6iBRPtg5XsiJjsnKEg7JuQ7IKw7KeAUSPgokUAAAA&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwiF7_GbwruFAxX8i68BHWE0DTsQ6BMoAHoECFEQAg">
                            원산지
                           </a>

                           </span>
                          </span>
